{% if factor.pack_id == "eu_cbam" -%}
CBAM embedded emissions for CN code {{ factor.cn_code }} per Regulation
(EU) 2023/956 Annex III (direct + indirect emissions methodology).
Functional unit: 1 tonne of the CN-coded good. Biogenic CO2 is excluded
from the CBAM value per Article 7(2). The pack enforces a CBAM-specific
cannot-resolve-safely contract so silent fallback to a global default is
blocked.
{% if factor.fallback_rank and factor.fallback_rank > 1 -%}

**Article 4(2) fallback notice.** Primary operator data was not
available, so an EU default value has been applied at fallback tier
{{ factor.fallback_rank }}. Justification:
{{ factor.article_4_2_justification }}. A CBAM surcharge may apply per
the definitive-regime implementing regulation.
{%- endif %}

{%- elif factor.pack_id == "eu_dpp" -%}
Digital Product Passport entry for product {{ factor.product_id }} per
Regulation (EU) 2024/1781 (ESPR). LCA boundary:
{{ factor.boundary }}. Biogenic CO2 reported separately. Per-product
delegated acts have not yet landed for every ESPR category, so the
inclusion list is intentionally open until the Commission publishes
category-specific DPP requirements.

{%- elif factor.pack_id == "eu_battery" -%}
EU Battery Regulation 2023/1542 Article 7 carbon-footprint declaration.
Battery class: {{ factor.battery_class }} (capacity
{{ factor.battery_energy_kwh }} kWh, weight {{ factor.battery_weight_kg }}
kg). Enforcement date: {{ factor.enforcement_date }}. DPP entry:
{{ factor.dpp_id }}. Functional unit: 1 kWh of energy delivered over the
battery service life per the harmonised CFP rules.
{%- endif %}

